idle xp
Discworld Creator Idle Xp Competition
idle xp

.SH Name
.SI 5
This document describes the idle xp competition for creators.
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Creators can attempt to collect idle xp for as long as possible, to gain the love and respect of their peers. If you die at any time, your xp count is reset, and everyone will mock you. Unless, of course, you are a Lord (see, not cheating now, is it Kili?).
.EP


